<section id="taxZone">
  <title><indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>tax zones</primary>

      <secondary>creating new</secondary>
    </indexterm>Tax Zone</title>

  <para>To create a new Tax Zone, select the NEW button. The following screen
  will appear:</para>

  <para><screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/taxZone.png" />
        </imageobject>

        <caption>Create New Tax Zone</caption>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot></para>

  <para>When creating a new Tax Zone, you are presented with the following
  options:</para>

  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Code</term>

      <listitem>
        <para>Enter a code to identify the Tax Zone.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry>
      <term>Description</term>

      <listitem>
        <para>Enter a description to describe the Tax Zone.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
</section>
